{"tid":274850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西鐵斬人 一男頭部中刀","createTime":"2017-06-07T15:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T12:55:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a85691c81941f244102e092452c566d73909409","tid":274850,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"西鐵線美孚站發生斬人血案，晚上9時許，兩名男乘客乘搭列車往屯門期間，因故發生爭執，初則口角，繼而動武，期間，有人從背囊取出利刀亂斬，其中一名男乘客頭部中刀流血。列車抵達美孚站後，兇徒奪門逃逸，傷者自行報警。現場消息指，有逾10名警員接報趕至現場，在各出入口調查，機動部隊亦出動，並帶同警犬在月台搜索，有警員更登上列車搜查，惟暫時未發現兇徒蹤影，傷者則由救護車送院治療。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97585b33a2d526f3a62936f80344c384cff431c","tid":274850,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/231306_4a4e20b65e81fc48c5c232d3cdc66664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F231306_4a4e20b65e81fc48c5c232d3cdc66664.jpg&h=03283d37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a42595231a4e670305991ebe80b9e1ddf4c6899","tid":274850,"uid":31368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"地鐵真係好危險，有咩都困獸鬥"},{"pid":"1d35ba4e45729de3ec910f15f56471ad1f0c067b","tid":274850,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"又會帶刀係身"},{"pid":"b4e53073bc3c57067c9c049ee2dcdfdbccb94fdb","tid":274850,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"繼兒動母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f042a89a06e031bc25158f564f3d4b8b6742307f","tid":274850,"uid":66714,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:14:55.000Z","msg":"幅圖明明係中環站黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5c8394a7a952b174627320f8f8b93c962cb291","tid":274850,"uid":117834,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"真係唔好周街同人嘈交 <br />\n<br />\n人地隨時袋住把刀 死左都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"eadd1189e253e09c65f5b11c1b131b7c1587302d","tid":274850,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幅圖明明係中環站黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來有兩單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日傍晚6時許，港鐵站亦有搜捕事件。一名德國籍遊客乘地鐵時，發現一名懷疑持槍的男子，在港島線月台登上往中環的列車，於是報警求助。警方接報到場調查，反恐特勤隊警員亦出動，正搜捕涉案可疑男子"},{"pid":"f5476d9c97916db040c02f417fcc67ddcbe78b64","tid":274850,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"沒預謀，應用八達通，死硬"},{"pid":"951126fe313c114effeb07478ec3ff602257a281","tid":274850,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"香港,唉,愈來愈多事端<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704cc0a65a6e68d162d6a381ea1b93a718a1bcb2","tid":274850,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/231306_4a4e20b65e81fc48c5c232d3cdc66664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F231306_4a4e20b65e81fc48c5c232d3cdc66664.jpg&h=03283d37&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n西鐵定地鐵"},{"pid":"3cf0d727df7e716cb677ecd41290a11c53fc1ebe","tid":274850,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ec274633065ada456a439951a38707be263a3e7","tid":274850,"uid":10680,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7a935a40394278f142534e0839b15c32aa24216","tid":274850,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shockin